<td valign="top">

<center><table width="96%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><col width="64"><col width="15"><tr><td bgcolor="f0f0f0f" background="25pxheading.gif" align="center" height="25"><font face="arial" color="000000" size="3"><b>Signs </b></font></td></tr><tr><td align="center"> <font size="2" face="arial">Posted By <a href="mailto:sean@data-zoid.com">Sean</a> on Sunday 29th December, 2002 @ 03:25 (Read: 322) &nbsp;<a href="printnews.php?id=53"><img src="http://www.data-zoid.com/brutallyhonest/images/print.gif" border="0" Alt="Printable Version"></a></font></td></tr><tr><td width="93%" valign="top"><div><br><font size="2" face="arial">
<a href="searchcat.php?cid=2">
<img src="http://www.data-zoid.com/brutallyhonest/images/category/" border="0" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10" alt="">
